Dear BLACKPINK 💖,

We are huge BLINKs from Sri Lanka, and we love you so much! There are so many fans here who are waiting, dreaming, and hoping to see you one day—not just for a concert, but even for a small fan meeting. We want you to know that your music, your energy, and your love have reached our hearts too.

We also love you 💕
We also want to see you 💫
We also have dreams to meet you one day 🫶🏽

If we had the money, we would travel just to see you—but sometimes it's not easy. That's why we are asking, from the bottom of our hearts, please come to Sri Lanka someday. Your visit would mean the world to us. We’ll be waiting with love, lightsticks, and full hearts. 🌸🇱🇰

With all our love,
Sri Lankan BLINKs 💗🖤

author: @aarnakapoor7037
text:
To BLACKPINK,
You’ve been my biggest inspiration ever since I discovered your music. Your strength, confidence, and powerful stage presence made me believe in myself. Because of you, I’ve found the courage to chase my dreams in music and performance.
Each of you has shown me what it means to be fierce, passionate, and unapologetically yourself. Whether it’s Jisoo’s elegance, Jennie’s charisma, Rosé’s soulful voice, or Lisa’s fiery dance — you’ve helped shape who I am today.
As you go on your 2nd world tour, I want you to know that you’ve changed my life, and one day, I hope to stand on the same stage as you.

And please, if possible — come to India!
There are so many BLINKs here who love you deeply and dream of seeing you live. I would be the happiest if I could see you perform in my own country. You have so many fans waiting for you with open hearts.

Thank you for being BLACKPINK.
With all my love,
AARNA ( a sincere BLINK)
FROM INDIA
